title: Eclipse Fill Part 2 (Laser Eraser & Pressbutton, The Spider,
description:
Ladies and gentlemennnnn, the starting lineup for your Eclipse Fill, Part Twoooooooooo:

Laser Eraser and Pressbutton 1-6 - A violent cyborg with the face of Ernest Borgnine teams with a cloned teen assassin! Features early work from David Lloyd and Steve Dillon.

Seduction of the Innocent 1-6 - Reprints of horror stories from the 50's.

The Spider 1-3 - Tim Truman and Enrique Alcatena update the classic pulp character.

The Spider: Reign of the Vampire King 1-3 - Same same and same same update same.


Many hosannas to the creative teams and scanners! Pick 'em up, lay 'em down!
